    return (
        <>

            BRIDAL CONCEPT

          <Typography variant="h6" align="center" color="inherit">

<Stack sx={{p:5}} direction="row">



    <Icon>

    </Icon>


<Icon> <ChatBubbleOutlineOutlined sx={{ml:2,mr:2,color:"#000000"}}/></Icon>
<Icon> <CalendarTodayOutlined sx={{ml:2,mr:2,color:"#000000"}}/></Icon>



</Stack>
       

          
       
         
        </Toolbar>
      </AppBar>
        </>

}

export default Heeder;
